ru.cos.sim.visualizer.frame
Class FrameDataHandler

java.lang.Object
  ru.cos.sim.visualizer.frame.FrameDataHandler

public class FrameDataHandler
extends Object

Handles frame data in the system. Contains information about parts of the trace, like nodes and segments, that are currently visible on the screen. According to this data simulation engine returns data about cars on the trace.

Author:
Dudinov Ivan
